      "body_md": "## Asset Command Centre v1.0.5 — Security Hardening (GA)\n\nCoordinated AuditToolkit suite security-hardening release.\n\n- OWASP hardening to a weighted **A+** scorecard\n- **Zero** Bandit high / medium / low findings\n- Container hardening (least-privilege, reduced attack surface)\n- Portable weighted OWASP scorer included\n- No breaking changes — upgrade in place via the native package\n\n**Assets:** native `.deb` / `.rpm`, customer-docs bundle, CycloneDX SBOM, `SHA256SUMS-1.0.5.txt`, and detached GPG `.asc` signatures (release key 926C3CBB).\n\nSuite: 2026.1 · Channel: GA\n",
